data.description: Escape to find serenity in this haven nestled in Copper Basin. Dive into community living with an array of amenities including a deluxe Clubhouse, state of the art exercise facility, pool, and heated spa. Inside this gem, bask in the sun-drenched beauty of this seamlessly flowing floorplan. An open design is the entertainer's dream, featuring a chic kitchen with stainless steel allure and opulent granite countertops. You're going to love the proximity to San Tan Valley's best shops, restaurants, and entertainment. Outdoor enthusiasts can enjoy the abundance of hiking trails at the nearby San Tan Mountains. This isn't just a home; it's a sanctuary a retreat of comfort, community, and nature, all at an irresistible price!
